	<div class="well well-lg">
		<p><h2>Technology Stack</h2></p>
		<p><h4>This site was developed using Rails 4 and Ruby 2. For deployment I used Heroku with a PostGres DataBase and the photo's are saved using S3 from Amazon Web Services. For uploading the photos I chose to use the Paperclip gem and the Devise gem was used for modeling Users. </h4></p>
		<p><h4>For the front-end I used Bootstrap 3 along with some coffescript. JQuery Masonary was used to give the photos that layered Pinterest look.</h4></p>
		<p><h4>You can see the project at my github page, <a href='https://github.com/mitchcail/internify'>github.com/mitchcail/internify</a></h4></p>
